@startuml
title 18 - Order Visibility Service - Consumidor Passivo da Jornada

autonumber
queue "Kafka" as Kafka
participant "Checkout Service" as Checkout
participant "Order Service" as Order
participant "Inventory Service" as Inventory
participant "Fulfillment Center Service" as FC
participant "Payment Service" as Payment
participant "Shipment Service" as Shipment
participant "Tracking Service" as Tracking
participant "Order Visibility Service" as OVS
database "order_visibility (Postgres)" as OvsDb
participant "SignalR Hub\n(/order-journeys/hub)" as Hub
participant "MarketplaceWeb\n(Order Monitor)" as UI

note over OVS
  OVS assina os mesmos tópicos consumidos pela saga, mas em um
  consumer group independente ("order-visibility-service"). Nunca
  publica comandos nem participa da saga — apenas projeta o estado.
end note

Checkout -> Kafka: checkout.confirmed
Kafka -> Order: checkout.confirmed
Kafka -> OVS: checkout.confirmed
activate OVS
OVS -> OvsDb: Cria order_journey por correlationId\n(orderId ainda nulo)
OVS -> Hub: OrderJourneyCreated
Hub -> UI: broadcast (grupo orders:all / correlation:{id})
deactivate OVS

Order -> Kafka: order.created
Kafka -> OVS: order.created
activate OVS
OVS -> OvsDb: Backfill orderId/checkoutId na jornada existente
OVS -> Hub: OrderJourneyUpdated
deactivate OVS

Inventory -> Kafka: inventory.reserved
FC -> Kafka: fulfillment.capacity.reserved
Payment -> Kafka: payment.approved
Kafka -> OVS: inventory.reserved / fulfillment.capacity.reserved / payment.approved
activate OVS
OVS -> OvsDb: Avança status + grava evento na timeline\n(idempotente por eventId, transação única)
OVS -> Hub: OrderJourneyUpdated (a cada evento)
deactivate OVS

Shipment -> Kafka: shipment.created
Tracking -> Kafka: shipment.status.updated
Kafka -> OVS: shipment.created / shipment.status.updated
activate OVS
OVS -> OvsDb: Status final (ex.: InTransit)
OVS -> Hub: OrderJourneyUpdated
deactivate OVS

UI -> OVS: GET /order-journeys/{orderId} (consulta sob demanda)
OVS --> UI: Status consolidado + timeline

note over OVS, UI
  Se OVS ficar indisponível, a saga em Order/Inventory/Fulfillment/
  Payment/Shipment/Tracking continua normalmente — apenas a tela
  operacional fica desatualizada.
end note

@enduml
